<div class="wp-block-group alignwide"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container"><!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>National Centre of Artificial Intelligence (Deep Learning Lab) organized the flagship program – Astera Data Integration Bootcamp’21, with collaboration with Astera. Aim of the workshop was to teach contemporary data management skills to the students.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Data drives all critical decisions in today’s business landscape. With this workshop aim was to teach some highly valued data management skills to the participants.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><strong><u>Skills learned:</u></strong></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:list {"ordered":true,"type":"1"} -->
<ol type="1"><li>Template-based data extraction method</li><li>Mining data from unstructured PDF documents</li><li>Converting unstructured data to structured data for querying and processing</li><li>Ensuring that the extracted data passes&nbsp;quality checks</li><li>Mapping data from source to target systems</li><li>Transforming raw data to make it consistent with the target schema</li><li>Translating business process into logical executable flows</li><li>Automating the entire process of data extraction and integration</li></ol>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>1-day <em><strong>Data Integration Bootcamp</strong></em> was conducted face to face in RIMMS seminar hall.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>
